<br />
<br />Please explain to me why this is a monumental problem that requires perverting the standard as opposed to just dealing with the overdump.
<br />
<br />According to bootgod's database, this is the ONLY game for which this is true. (Although it is also true of the Game Genie ROM.)</div>

